<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-6 sm:py-8" style="view-transition-name: page-content;">
  <header class="mb-8">
    <a href="/" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm mb-4">&larr; Back</a>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-base-content/60 mt-2">Last updated: <%= Date.today.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
  </header>

  <div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none">
    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

    <h3>Account Information</h3>
    <p>When you sign in with Google, we collect:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your name</li>
      <li>Email address</li>
      <li>Profile picture URL</li>
      <li>Google account identifier</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Content You Provide</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Videos you upload for analysis</li>
      <li>Comments and stories you create</li>
      <li>Voice notes and images</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Automatically Collected Information</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Usage data and interaction logs</li>
      <li>Browser type and device information</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your information to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Provide and improve the Service</li>
      <li>Authenticate your account</li>
      <li>Process and analyze your video content</li>
      <li>Generate AI-powered scripts and audio</li>
      <li>Send notifications (with your consent)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google Gemini AI</strong> - For video analysis and text-to-speech generation</li>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare Stream</strong> - For video hosting and delivery</li>
      <li><strong>Google OAuth</strong> - For authentication</li>
    </ul>
    <p>These services have their own privacy policies governing their use of your data.</p>

    <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Video analysis sessions are automatically deleted after 30 minutes</li>
      <li>Uploaded videos sent to Gemini are processed and not permanently stored by the AI</li>
      <li>Account data is retained until you request deletion</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
    <p>
      We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data. However, no method of
      transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Access your personal data</li>
      <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
      <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent for data processing</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>7. Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      We use session cookies to maintain your login state. We do not use tracking or advertising cookies.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      The Service is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children.
    </p>

    <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of significant changes.
    </p>

    <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy-related questions or to exercise your rights, please contact us through the application.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
